---
---

<section class="founder" id="story" aria-labelledby="founder-title">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="founder__layout">
      <!-- Visual -->
      <figure class="founder__media reveal">
        <video
          class="founder__video"
          autoplay
          muted
          loop
          playsinline
          preload="metadata"
          poster="/images/founder.jpg"
        >
          <source src="/videos/founder.mov" type="video/quicktime" />
          <source src="/videos/founder.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
        <div class="founder__media-veil"></div>
        <figcaption class="founder__caption">
          <span class="caps--wide">The Walking CEO</span>
          <strong>Peter Barta · Founder</strong>
        </figcaption>
        <div class="founder__brackets" aria-hidden="true">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </div>
      </figure>

      <!-- Copy -->
      <div class="founder__copy">
        <p class="eyebrow reveal">Built by its founder</p>
        <h2 id="founder-title" class="founder__title split">
          {'Two-time cancer survivor.'.split(' ').map((w) => (<span class="split__word"><span>{w}</span></span>))}
          <br />
          <em>{'Everest Marathon at 40.'.split(' ').map((w) => (<span class="split__word"><span>{w}</span></span>))}</em>
        </h2>

        <div class="founder__quote reveal" data-stagger="2">
          <p>
            “I didn't find a product that acknowledged what my clients'
            bodies were actually doing — cycling, taper, recovery, peri-menopause.
            So I built one with the science team I trust, in a facility
            that meets pharmaceutical standards, and published the doses
            on the front of the sachet.”
          </p>
          <cite>— Peter Barta, PN-Certified</cite>
        </div>

        <ul class="founder__facts">
          <li class="reveal" data-stagger="3"><span>EU GMP</span> Vitema manufacturing, Certificate of Analysis on every PDP</li>
          <li class="reveal" data-stagger="4"><span>PN-Certified</span> Coach and nutrition practitioner</li>
          <li class="reveal" data-stagger="5"><span>Transparent</span> Founder story published, reachable, never pseudonymous</li>
          <li class="reveal" data-stagger="6"><span>Field-tested</span> Protocols refined through direct coaching, not marketing focus groups</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="founder__actions reveal" data-stagger="6">
          <a href="#substack" class="btn btn--ghost" data-hover>
            <span>Read the full story</span>
            <svg class="arrow" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M1 7h12M8 2l5 5-5 5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#products" class="btn btn--copper" data-hover>
            <span>Start with BALANCE</span>
            <svg class="arrow" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M1 7h12M8 2l5 5-5 5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .founder {
    background: var(--xyv-black-deep);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .founder::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 20%;
    width: 50%;
    height: 60%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at left, rgba(184, 115, 51, 0.08), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .founder__layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-8);
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* ---------- Media ---------- */
  .founder__media {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg), var(--shadow-inset);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .founder__video {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    filter: grayscale(0.65) contrast(1.1) saturate(0.85);
    transition: filter var(--dur-slow) var(--ease-smooth);
  }

  .founder__media:hover .founder__video { filter: grayscale(0.1) contrast(1.1) saturate(1); }

  .founder__media-veil {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(11, 11, 12, 0.15) 40%, rgba(11, 11, 12, 0.8) 100%);
  }

  .founder__caption {
    position: absolute;
    left: var(--sp-5);
    bottom: var(--sp-5);
    right: var(--sp-5);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
    color: var(--xyv-off-white);
  }

  .founder__caption .caps--wide { color: var(--xyv-copper); font-size: 0.65rem; }
  .founder__caption strong { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; }

  .founder__brackets span {
    position: absolute;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--xyv-copper);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .founder__brackets span:nth-child(1) { top: var(--sp-3); left: var(--sp-3); border-right: 0; border-bottom: 0; }
  .founder__brackets span:nth-child(2) { top: var(--sp-3); right: var(--sp-3); border-left: 0; border-bottom: 0; }
  .founder__brackets span:nth-child(3) { bottom: var(--sp-3); left: var(--sp-3); border-right: 0; border-top: 0; }
  .founder__brackets span:nth-child(4) { bottom: var(--sp-3); right: var(--sp-3); border-left: 0; border-top: 0; }

  /* ---------- Copy ---------- */
  .founder__copy {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-5);
  }

  .founder__title {
    font-size: var(--fs-display);
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .founder__title em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--xyv-copper);
  }

  .founder__quote {
    padding: var(--sp-5) var(--sp-6);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--xyv-copper);
    background: var(--xyv-black-soft);
    border-radius: 0 var(--r-md) var(--r-md) 0;
  }

  .founder__quote p {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--fs-lead);
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .founder__quote cite {
    display: block;
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    color: var(--xyv-copper);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-caps);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .founder__facts {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-5) var(--sp-6);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--xyv-line);
    padding-top: var(--sp-6);
  }

  .founder__facts li {
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .founder__facts span {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-caps);
    color: var(--xyv-copper);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-1);
  }

  .founder__actions {
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: var(--sp-3);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding-top: var(--sp-3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .founder__layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .founder__facts { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .founder__copy { align-items: center; text-align: center; }
    .founder__title { margin-inline: auto; }

    .founder__quote {
      border-left: 0;
      border-top: 2px solid var(--xyv-copper);
      border-radius: var(--r-md);
      padding: var(--sp-6) var(--sp-5) var(--sp-5);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .founder__quote cite { text-align: center; }

    .founder__facts {
      gap: var(--sp-5);
      padding-top: var(--sp-6);
    }
    .founder__facts li { text-align: center; }
    .founder__facts li span { margin-inline: auto; }

    .founder__actions { justify-content: center; width: 100%; }
    .founder__caption { text-align: center; align-items: center; }
  }
</style>
